milestones.description: This is the lowest match aggregate (203) involving teams Zimbabwe & Kenya in ODIs

stories.title: Only when I laugh
stories.subTitle: Zimbabwe v Kenya, 3rd ODI, Harare
stories.summary: Fans were reduced to ironic cheering as Zimbabwe were thrashed by Kenya at Harare Sports Club ... and many more familiar faces were reduced to the role of spectators

stories.title: Harper upbeat but Curran fumes
stories.subTitle: Zimbabwe v Kenya, 3rd ODI, Harare
stories.summary: The reaction of Zimbabwe's and Kenya's coaches and captains could not have been more marked after Zimbabwe's humiliation in the third ODI at Harare

stories.title: Zimbabwe's inexperience cruelly exposed by Kenya
stories.subTitle: Zimbabwe v Kenya, 3rd ODI, Harare
stories.summary: Zimbabwe lost six wickets for five runs as they were bowled out for 69 by Kenya in the third ODI at Harare, losing by 65 runs to go 2-1 down in the five-match series
